## Payment System

### Stripe Integration ([`internal/payment/stripe/`](internal/payment/stripe/))

- **Dual Stripe accounts:** Production (`CARD`) and test (`CARD_TEST`) processors run simultaneously
- **Pre-order PaymentIntent flow:** PaymentIntents are created before order submission for card payments, then associated with the order
- **Payment monitoring:** Background goroutines monitor pending payments for completion
- **Refunds:** Full and partial refunds with per-item tracking
- **Reconciliation worker:** Cleans up orphaned pre-order PaymentIntents

### Supported Payment Methods

Defined in entity layer: `CARD`, `CARD_TEST`, `BANK_INVOICE`, `CASH`

---

## Analytics Pipeline

### GA4 + BigQuery ([`internal/analytics/`](internal/analytics/))

- **GA4 Data API client** — Fetches daily metrics, product page views, country sessions, ecommerce data
- **BigQuery client** — Runs complex analytics queries (funnel analysis, user journeys, device funnels, engagement metrics, error tracking, etc.)
- **GA4 sync worker** — Periodically syncs GA4 and BigQuery data into MySQL cache tables for fast dashboard queries
- **Circuit breaker** — Protects against GA4/BigQuery outages with configurable failure thresholds
- **BQ cache store** — Read/write MySQL cache for precomputed BigQuery analytics

### Business Metrics ([`internal/store/metrics*.go`](internal/store/metrics.go))

- Core sales metrics (revenue, AOV, conversion rates)
- Customer metrics (new vs returning, LTV)
- Geographic breakdown
- Time series analysis
- Cohort retention, order sequence, revenue Pareto
- Inventory health, size run efficiency
- Product trends, dead stock, slow movers

